videos.headline: Fumble extends gain for Vanderbilt after long run
videos.description: After a 19-yard run, Vanderbilt RB Ralph Webb gets hit and fumbles, but his teammate C.J. Duncan scoops the loose ball and gains another 12 yards for Vandy.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt stops option on fourth down
videos.description: Vanderbilt's defense sniffs out the Ole Miss option as Jordan Griffin tackles Jordan Wilkins behind the line-of-scrimmage to keep the game scoreless.

videos.headline: Brown takes slant to the house
videos.description: Ole Miss takes the 7-0 lead after A.J. Brown runs a slant route and takes it 58 yards to the end zone.

videos.headline: Webb turns on burners for tying TD
videos.description: Vanderbilt RB Ralph Webb finds a hole and takes it 38 yards to the end zone tying Ole Miss 7-7 in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Sherfield comes down with great catch in bounds
videos.description: Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur throws it up for Trent Sherifeld who climbs the ladder to make the 38-yard catch.

videos.headline: Webb scores second TD on second effort
videos.description: Vanderbilt RB Ralph Webb takes the hand-off and tries to jump the pile, but lands on his feet and fights past the goal line to give Vanderbilt a 14-7 lead.

videos.headline: Lodge shakes free for wide-open TD
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson fires a 35-yard pass downfield to DaMarkus Lodge who is standing alone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Ole Miss defense forces strip-sack
videos.description: Ole Miss DL Maquis Haynes sacks the quarterback and the fumble is recovered by Ole Miss in Vanderbilt territory.

videos.headline: Ole Miss QB runs over defender for TD
videos.description: Shea Patterson scrambles to his left and runs over the Vanderbilt defender to cross the goal line giving Ole Miss a 21-14 lead.

videos.headline: Metcalf makes insane catch around DB's helmet
videos.description: Ole Miss receiver D.K. Metcalf goes up and around the Vanderbilt defender to hold on to the insane catch.

videos.headline: Wilkins jumps and fights for TD
videos.description: Ole Miss RB Jordan Wilkins takes the hand-off and jumps free to the end zone on an 18-yard scoring run.

videos.headline: Patterson connects with Lodge on quick TD
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson finds DaMarkus Lodge for another score to give Ole Miss a 35-14 lead.

videos.headline: Shurmur finds Lipscomb underneath for score before half
videos.description: Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur fires it to Kalija Lipscomb for a 13-yard score.

videos.headline: Ole Miss scoring quick to put up 35 in first half
videos.description: Ole Miss head coach Matt Luke says that he likes the energy his team is playing with and hopes it increases in the second half.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt defense needs to be more aware in second half
videos.description: Vanderbilt head coach Derek Mason says that he can live with the 50-50 balls not going his team's way, but he wants his players to focus more on their assignments in the second half.

videos.headline: Ole Miss defense forces safety
videos.description: Ole Miss DL Marquis Haynes forces another fumble while sacking QB Kyle Shurmer as Vanderbilt jumps on the loose ball for a safety.

videos.headline: Brown catches second TD
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson's play-action fake  frees A.J. Brown for the 29-yard score.

videos.headline: Shurmur fakes, finds Pinkney for TD
videos.description: Vanderbilt QB Kyle Shurmur fakes the hand-off on the goal line and finds a wide-open Jared Pinkney for the score.

videos.headline: Swinney scores 55-yard TD
videos.description: Vanderbilt RB Eric Swinney sprints to the left sideline and outruns the Ole Miss defense for a touchdown making it 57-28.
